<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>New User Registration - SendIt Admin</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2c3e50;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #34495e 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 35px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><polygon points="50,20 80,80 20,80" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="30" cy="40" r="3" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="70" cy="60" r="2" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.15;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: 700;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 8px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            opacity: 0.9;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .notification-badge {
            background: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.3);
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
        .admin-badge {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: white;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 12px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }
        .user-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background: #5a6fd8;
        }
        .button.secondary {
            background: #6c757d;
        }
        .button.secondary:hover {
            background: #5a6268;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .stats {
            background: #e8f4fd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stats h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #3498db;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="notification-badge">NEW USER</div>
            <h1>ðŸ‘‹ New User Registration</h1>
            <p>A new user has joined SendIt!</p>
            <div class="admin-badge">ðŸ”” Admin Notification</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="user-details">
            <h3>ðŸ“‹ User Information</h3>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Name:</span>
                <span class="detail-value"><%= newUserName %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Email:</span>
                <span class="detail-value"><%= newUserEmail %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Role:</span>
                <span class="detail-value"><%= newUserRole %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Registration Date:</span>
                <span class="detail-value"><%= registrationDate %></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats">
            <h3>ðŸ“Š Quick Stats</h3>
            <p>This user will be able to:</p>
            <ul style="text-align: left; margin: 10px 0;">
                <li>Create and track parcels</li>
                <li>View delivery maps</li>
                <li>Receive real-time updates</li>
                <li>Access their delivery history</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="<%= process.env.ADMIN_DASHBOARD_URL || 'http://localhost:4200/admin' %>" class="button">
                View in Admin Dashboard
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:<%= newUserEmail %>" class="button secondary">
                Send Welcome Email
            </a>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
            <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #856404;">ðŸ’¡ Pro Tip</h4>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #856404;">
                Consider reaching out to new users personally to welcome them and offer assistance. 
                This can significantly improve user retention and satisfaction.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© 2025 SendIt. Making shipping simple since 2018.</p>
            <p>This notification was sent to <%= adminEmail %></p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8em; margin-top: 10px;">
                You can manage email notifications in your admin settings.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 